					Thank you for agreeing to participate as a speaker at <a href="/europe/2015">LendIt Europe 2015</a>. We have created this Speaker Information page to provide you with details and instructions to help you prepare for the conference. We will be updating this page with additional information as we get closer to the event; you will be notified by email when we make any changes.
				</p>
				<p>
